Package: ALSroads
Type: Package
Title: Road alignment and measure from airborne LiDAR data for MFFP
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Jean-Romain Roussel
Maintainer: Jean-Romain Roussel <jean-romain.roussel.1@ulaval.ca>
Description: Functions to realign miss-positionned roads from a maintained map of roads 
  and to compute some state metrics such as the state of the roads (exist, no longer exist)
  as well as their width, drivable width, slope and so on.
